item.title: Git_synctips
item.description: The remote repository has changed and the local repository has not changed. git remote -v git fetch origin master git log master.. origin/master git merge origin/master The remote repository has not changed and the local repository has changed. git add -A or git add . or git add –all git commit -m “the content of your modify” git push -u origin master
